dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Willie Clark. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Janet Scott.
Nice to meet you, Janet. Could you please provide me with the number of vehicles covered under your policy?
I have two vehicles under my policy.
Thank you, Janet. Can you also confirm the number of additional drivers listed on your policy?
There are three additional drivers listed.
Thank you for providing that information, Janet. Is there anything else you would like to inquire about or update on your policy today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Janet. Thank you for reaching out to us today. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to contact us again. Have a great day!
